25
00:00:54,800 --> 00:00:56,280
I'll give you the same
acupuncture treatment as yesterday.

26
00:00:56,480 --> 00:00:57,237
Be careful.

27
00:00:57,320 --> 00:00:58,717
You're a loyal student

28
