30
00:01:04,640 --> 00:01:05,520
No.

31
00:01:06,440 --> 00:01:07,360
Who's my mother?

32
00:01:10,440 --> 00:01:11,400
Little Lark?

33
00:01:14,040 --> 00:01:14,920
Who?

34
00:01:17,680 --> 00:01:18,560
Fine.

35
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:22,760
When I ask you about something,

36
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:23,960
you don't remember.

37
00:01:24,360 --> 00:01:25,157
And, I can't follow your bidding

38
00:01:25,240 --> 00:01:26,040
without being worried.

39
00:01:26,480 --> 00:01:27,277
We'll never

40
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:28,800
be on the same page.

41
00:01:30,520 --> 00:01:33,320
We should stick to
your master's instructions.

42
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:41,640
If only he was the one
with amnesia instead.

43
00:01:43,520 --> 00:01:44,320
I guess

44
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:46,240
